          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1595251241663-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar, </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> water </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a separate bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
